name: Pushing and Pulling #2
description:
You are progressing from the threshold pushing efforts you are familiar with but introducing some pulling intervals. These are completed at a power above your FTP. 



If the pushing intervals are designed to push your threshold up from below, these effectively pull your threshold up from above.
